# Cluster causal chain (Sub-BN diagnosis)
@cluster-failure-chain (1) cron 5m fires concurrent kicks on Mac. (2) hexa_remote tries external SSH (hetzner/ubu/ubu2). (3) per-host slot pool exhausted → exit 64. (4) resolver sees rc=64 → neg_cache_set 60s. (5) next kick hits docker fallback. (6) Sub-BO probes container → no node → rc=76. (7) kick fails, no witness, Sub-BN rate++.
@cluster-failure-fix-direction Sub-BR — slot-aware cron throttle: 5m cron should query hexa_remote slot status before firing N parallel kicks; emit __KICK_DEFERRED__ instead of exit-64-cascade.
@cluster-failure-fix-direction-alt Sub-BS — per-host slot expansion: raise hetzner heavy_concurrency limit if 124GB RAM headroom permits; check current vs PSI ceiling.

